These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, martial-arts
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, tram
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | martial-arts |
| Transport     | tram | airplane  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: apricot, strawberry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, soccer
1. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | apricot      | strawberry         |
| Sport   | cycling | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
There 2 different types of food: kale, pumpkin
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | fanta | coffee   |
| Food       | pumpkin  | kale |

 #################################

 
